	<div style="text-align:right;">
		CORREIA, Isadora Mudrei<sup>1</sup>; DUARTE, Francisco Carlos<sup>2</sup>		<BR>
		PIBIC		- Bolsa PUCPR-PIBIC		<BR>
		<I>--</I>
